OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FSharp End's Rob Osborne explored the
OL,7,Fbenefits, and concerns, of hydrogen
OL,9,FA hydrogen project in has been given
OL,10,Fthe 'green light' and awarded UK
OL,11,FGovernment funding - but some nearby
OL,12,Fresidents fear explosions coming from
OL,13,Fthe plant.
OL,15,FWith the Welsh Government's Net Zero
OL,16,Ftarget for 2050, hydrogen provide a
OL,17,Fsolution to hit its goal.
