OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FIt's produced through the electrolysis
OL,7,Fof water using renewable energy
OL,8,Fsources and can be stored and used as
OL,9,Fneeded.
OL,11,FThe Hybont plant, planned for a site
OL,12,Fnext to Brynmenyn Industrial Estate,
OL,13,Fis being supported by a #750,000 grant
OL,14,Ffrom UK Government.
OL,16,FNearby resident Chris Owens, told
OL,17,FITV's Sharp End: "We feel that we're
OL,18,Fbeing used as a guinea pig and this is
OL,19,Fbeing dumped on us."
