OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FSafety is top of his list of concerns
OL,7,Fand is one of the reasons why he is
OL,8,Fpart of the 'Say No To Hybont'
OL,9,Fcampaign locally.
OL,11,FHe added: "They're saying this is
OL,12,Fgoing to be like a petrol station, but
OL,13,Fit's hydrogen held under pressure
OL,14,Fabove ground and hydrogen is very
OL,15,Fexplosive so there could be a major
OL,16,Fincident."
OL,18,FBridgend councillor Timothy Thomas
OL,19,Fsays his constituents are concerned
OL,20,Fabout the plant's close proximity to
OL,21,Fresidential areas.
