OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FHe said: "The proposed plant is within
OL,7,F50 metres of residential zones. There
OL,8,Fare concerns about the impact it could
OL,9,Fhave on local businesses during the
OL,10,Ftwo years of construction."
OL,12,FIf given the go-ahead, the development
OL,13,Fwould include a green hydrogen
OL,14,Fproduction facility with
OL,15,Felectrolysers, hydrogen storage, a
OL,16,Fhydrogen refuelling station, plus a
OL,17,FhydrogenJpipeline.
