OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FIt is said to create up to 130
OL,7,Fconstruction jobs and five specialist
OL,8,Fjobs once complete to maintain and
OL,9,Foperate the facility.
OL,11,FHydrogen produced at such facilities
OL,12,Fcan be used as a fuel for vehicles
OL,13,Fsuch as trucks, busses, ferries,
OL,14,Ftrains and other heavy transport -
OL,15,Fwhich investor Marubeni Europower says
OL,16,Fwill help reduce the country's
OL,17,Fdependence on fossil fuels and helping
OL,18,Fto lower emissions from the
OL,19,Ftransportation sector.
