OL,6,FGeorge Dodd, Senior Vice-Preisdent of
OL,7,FMarubeni Europower, said: "There are
OL,8,Fwell established codes and standards
OL,9,Fabout how to use, produce and store
OL,10,Fhydrogen safely. So the project will,
OL,11,Fof course, follow those standards.
OL,13,F"I think it's got a great opportunity
OL,14,Fto help us in our decarbonisation
OL,15,Fpathway.
