OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,F"As we look to reduce carbon dioxide
OL,7,Femissions, there are applications that
OL,8,Fare difficult to electrify. But the
OL,9,Fenergy demands of heavy goods vehicles
OL,10,Fare a bit beyond what batteries can
OL,11,Fdeliver today, and some of our
OL,12,Findustrial mechanisms can't be
OL,13,Felectrified - I believe hydrogen has a
OL,14,Fbig contribution to play."
OL,16,FWhat is hydrogen?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
