OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FProfessor Jon Maddy, Director of the
OL,7,FHydrogen Centre and academic lead for
OL,8,FSouth Wales Industrial Cluster, said:
OL,9,F"Hydrogen is a fuel and like any fuel
OL,10,Fyou can combust it and with combusting
OL,11,Fyou can gain energy and convert that
OL,12,Finto heat and movement.
OL,14,F"The benefit of hydrogen compared to
OL,15,Ffossil fuels, or carbon-containing
OL,16,Ffuels, is that you don't get any
OL,17,Fcarbon emissions from that process
OL,18,Fitself."
