OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FHydrogen is currently produced and
OL,7,Fused in other projects across the UK,
OL,8,Fincluding Aberdeen City Council and
OL,9,Ftheir bus fleet, Wright Bus in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and HydroFLEX in
OL,11,FBirmingham.
OL,13,FIt's hoped the Brynmenyn site would
OL,14,Fprovide fuel for buses and large
OL,15,Fvehicles such as gritters.
OL,17,FChris Foxall, CEO of Hyppo, says
OL,18,Fhydrogen vehicles are classed as being
OL,19,F"even safer than diesel and petrol".
