OL,3,C'Fears of explosions' as green
OL,4,Chydrogen plant proposed 50m from homes
OL,6,FHe added: "When you force a single
OL,7,Ftechnology into a community it can be
OL,8,Fquite difficult, but if there's
OL,9,Foptions for people, they get to
OL,10,Fexperience hydrogen and it works for
OL,11,Fthem, then all of a sudden they've got
OL,12,Fa voice and politicians will listen to
OL,13,Fthat.
OL,15,F"So what we're trying to do is get
OL,16,Fbuses on the road, get passengers on
OL,17,Fthe buses, get cars on the road, get
OL,18,Fpassengers in the cars and every time
OL,19,Fsomeone gets into a car they say 'this
OL,20,Fis brilliant' - why aren't we doing
OL,21,Fmore of this?"
